snippet.title: Best VGM 1007 - Cthulhu Saves the World - Existence Collapses (Final Boss)
snippet.description:
Download the free OST here : http://www.binbag.superfundungeonrun.com/CStW_OST.zip

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PC
Cthulhu Saves the World (2010)
Existence Collapses (Final Boss)
Gordon McNeil
